# ImpactConnect: Smart Resource Allocation Command Center
🚀 **Data-Driven Volunteer Coordination for Social Impact**

ImpactConnect is a high-performance, AI-powered platform designed for NGOs to digitize community needs and intelligently allocate volunteer resources. Built for the **Google Solution Challenge 2026**, it leverages Google Cloud Vision AI and Gemini 1.5 Flash to transform fragmented field data into actionable social impact.

